{"type":"message","id":"481005f1","parentId":"5771f23e","timestamp":"2026-02-27T06:55:42.945Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户说嘟啦是他女朋友，让我去她毕业那条帖子下面评论逗她一下。\n\n看她的笔记列表，\"BNU 变 NYU💜\"（146 赞）应该是毕业相关的帖子，从北师大到纽约大学。这条是 e7。\n\n我需要：\n1. 点进这个帖子\n2. 找到评论框\n3. 写个逗她的评论\n\n既然是用户女朋友，评论应该友善、好玩一点，别太恶臭。可以调侃一下从北师大到 NYU 的学历提升，或者调侃一下用户（她男朋友）之类的。\n\n先点进帖子。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"操，原来是你女朋友啊！行，我去她\"BNU 变 NYU💜\"那条下面逗逗她。\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_ff8cac31320f4a3990601a7a","name":"browser","arguments":{"action":"act","request":{"kind":"click","ref":"e7"},"targetId":"608BFDA4AC68646CCEC15B8A9C232828"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":117042,"output":381,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":117423,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772175309849}}
