{"type":"message","id":"3b42a793","parentId":"63f204c9","timestamp":"2026-02-27T07:01:40.755Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"帖子链接还是打不开，显示访问链接异常，可能帖子私密了。换个能看的帖子，第一个滑雪帖子 e5 有完整 URL，试试那个。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"操，又 404 了，\"访问链接异常\"。这帖子真看不了。\n\n兄弟，要不我去她第一个帖子\"🏂还有谁不会拍滑雪转场！？\"下面评论？那个 URL 是 `/user/profile/5b57d22811be105db2fcf544/69633a2b000000001a03201b`，应该能打开。你想让我评论啥？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":138551,"output":184,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":138735,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772175693712}}
