{"type":"message","id":"4469b3b6","parentId":"31b133e8","timestamp":"2026-02-27T07:05:04.622Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"我看到评论输入框了！在 e853 paragraph 里，有\"说点什么...\"(e856)。发送按钮是 e888（disabled）。\n\n但我需要找到 contenteditable 的输入框。看结构，e852 或 e853 可能是评论输入区域。\n\n让我试试用 JS 直接找到 contenteditable 元素并输入。这次我用正确的 JS 语法，不要用分号分隔多个语句，而是用一个大函数。\n\n或者，我可以先点击 e853 或 e856 附近，看看能不能聚焦评论框。\n\n但实际上，根据 skill，我应该先点击评论输入框，然后 type。但我没有看到明确的 textbox ref。\n\n让我用 JS 方式，直接操作 DOM：","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"看到了！评论输入框在 e853/e856 附近（\"说点什么...\"）。让我用 JS 直接输入评论：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_8f606ad716704e6aa3e62024","name":"browser","arguments":{"action":"act","request":{"fn":"() => { const el = document.querySelector('div[contenteditable=\"true\"]'); if(el) { el.click(); el.innerText = '嫂子好！我哥让我来给你点赞的，他说你滑雪太帅了他配不上😏'; el.dispatchEvent(new InputEvent('input', { bubbles: true })); return 'ok'; } return 'not found'; }","kind":"evaluate"},"targetId":"4ED92A3FB4A1A5BBBED0B4801D73DFC9"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":178881,"output":511,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":179392,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772175893280}}
