{"type":"message","id":"c4d1fd10","parentId":"f30950df","timestamp":"2026-02-27T07:07:43.180Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"看到了！评论区域在 e850-e889 这块。e853 是 paragraph，e856 是\"说点什么...\"文本。发送按钮是 e888（disabled）。我需要找到评论输入框，可能是一个 hidden 的 input 或者 contenteditable div。让我用 JS 直接找 comment input 并点击它。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"看到了！评论区域在底部，e856 是\"说点什么...\"，e888 是发送按钮（disabled）。但我没看到明确的输入框 ref。让我用 JS 先清空搜索框，然后找真正的评论输入框并点击它：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_09486035fcba46bdb956bc41","name":"browser","arguments":{"action":"act","request":{"fn":"() => { document.querySelector('input[type=\"text\"]').value = ''; const commentArea = document.querySelector('#comment-textarea, .comment-input, .comment-box, [placeholder*=\"评论\"], [placeholder*=\"说点什么\"]'); if(commentArea) { commentArea.click(); return 'clicked comment area'; } const inputs = document.querySelectorAll('input, textarea, [contenteditable]'); for(let el of inputs) { const rect = el.getBoundingClientRect(); if(rect.bottom > window.innerHeight - 100 && el.type !== 'hidden') { el.click(); return 'clicked bottom input: ' + el.tagName; } } return 'no comment input found'; }","kind":"evaluate"},"targetId":"4ED92A3FB4A1A5BBBED0B4801D73DFC9"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":213848,"output":434,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":214282,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772176046331}}
